title: See You Again
lyrics: ...meoljjeonghae gojak handaneun mal geuge jeonbuni neo apasseumyeon seo usjiman nae nunen da boyeo ...eotteohge jinaessni bogodo molla da neo ttaemunijan ha jal jinaes seul ri eopsjan ha jalhaess da geu reogil jalhaess da he eojimyeon da doel jul aras seo sasil bogo sipeos seo neujeossjiman dasi manna ja uri cheoeumbuteo sijakhaebo ja geuttaecheoreom apeugo dachyeodo dasi mannal tenik ka gyeol guk saranghal teni kka mian hae nae ga da mian hae geu mari mwoga eoryeowossneun ji neomu orae geollyeos seo neujeossjiman dasi manna ja uri cheoeumbuteo sijakhaebo ja geuttaecheoreom apeugo dachyeodo dasi mannal tenik ka gyeol guk saranghal teni kka nae mari manheun du nuni ana dal la hajanha swipjin anhji man uri myeot beonigo saranghaebo ja eochapi nal butjapgo magado neoe ge gal teni kka geuman mianhae i baboya geunyang naegero dorawa oraenmane kkok anabo ja uri majimakcheoreom neol sarang hae babocheoreom sogado gwaenchanha dasi neoil geojan ha gyeol guk saranghal geojan ha eonjenga tto miwojindae do sarangha ja
